---
layout: layout.njk
title: Survivor Stories
description: "Stories of survivors and their families, shared in their own words — from crisis to healing, with The Caring Place's support."
---
<div class="pagehero" style="background-image:url('https://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_3FbWkBIBY3yHx2BErgPM2PJzng4/hf_20260707_222126_48a897bd-5c85-47e7-9386-ffa53c002807.png')">
  <div class="shade"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Survivor Stories</p>
    <p class="eyebrow">In Their Own Words</p>
    <h1>Survivor Stories</h1>
    <p>Every survivor's path is different. These stories are shared with permission, in hope that they might help someone else feel less alone.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for story in stories %}
      <div class="card">
        <span class="role">{{ story.byline }}</span>
        <h3><a href="/survivor-stories/{{ story.slug }}/" style="text-decoration:none">{{ story.name }}'s Story</a></h3>
        <p>{{ story.summary }}</p>
        <a href="/survivor-stories/{{ story.slug }}/" style="font-weight:700;display:inline-block;margin-top:10px">Read {{ story.name }}'s story →</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:44px;font-size:15px;color:rgb(46 42 49 / .6)">Note for the client: these profiles carry forward what's currently published. If you have the fuller original narratives on file, send them over and we'll expand each page.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="ctaband" style="background-image:url('https://d8j0ntlcm91z4.cloudfront.net/user_3FbWkBIBY3yHx2BErgPM2PJzng4/hf_20260707_222125_c8758362-9543-4359-9436-60073c500282.png')">
  <div class="shade"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="small">You are not alone</p>
    <h2>Free, confidential help is available 24/7</h2>
    <a class="btn btn-clay" href="/get-help/">Get help now</a>
  </div>
</div>
